article_id:653,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Facility Event, A Crescendo of Courage, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/059961c7f6cd8b60a8980b0b7e44533b.png,message:<div>A new facility event, A Crescendo of Courage, will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1565676000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>This event will pit your group of adventurers against bosses of the shadow element. You&rsquo;ll also be able to build an event-related reward facility for your Halidom!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/059961c7f6cd8b60a8980b0b7e44533b.png"></div><div>The summer, the beach, and a stage make a beautiful backdrop for Siren&#39;s dream concert! It&#39;s on the Prince and friends to build a stage and gather spectators...but this task will prove to be challenging. Will Siren be able to share her song with the masses? The summer still has a lot in store for the Prince and friends!</div><div><br></div><div>â–  Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1565676000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1566453599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1565589600,update_time1569483582